{"TopicId":197377,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"SpeedTree and ASTRONEER-like clouds for KSP2.","CreatedByName":"Vegatoxi","CreatedById":134066,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-09T06:11:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vegatoxi","CreatedById":134066,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-09T06:11:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022205123\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/205123-nate-simpson/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Nate Simpson\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEveryone know that KSP is lack of clouds and environement.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd in 2021 it\u0027s very sensitive part of game like KSP, where you explore different places.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople want to see living world and now just a colored brick...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m barrely can call a game with good trees but Witcher 3 defenitely one of it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd they use SpeedTree for it:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://store.speedtree.com\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://store.speedtree.com\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Which also have native unity support.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll be glad to see same picture in KSP2 (maybe more cartoon than it but\u00A0same density)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224Wodoim.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/4Wodoim.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame here with clouds.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can call only 2 games with enough good clouds: War Thunder and ASTRONEER. Also last MSFS probably but i dont play it yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut in case that KSP more cartoon than realistic - ASTRONEER style clouds will perfectly fit in it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/JUgcO8epFaE?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope that\u00A0devs pay enough attention to these\u00A0things.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}